" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cPM5mtU8PBY</a>"},{"pid":"1af1e55dc9cafe618d686e3941050ede32dba080","tid":443613,"uid":136590,"like":3,"dislike":19,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:19:54.000Z","msg":"你咩都唔會望到，因為你到光速個下已經死左<br />\n構成身體嘅原子係到光速個下就會解體<br />\n仲有當你到達光速時間係會完全停止，所以你連擰轉頭呢個動作都唔會做到"},{"pid":"67f2e43c9055c95c5f1461f3c9d5fab2ace44e2d","tid":443613,"uid":92278,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:21:50.000Z","msg":"會望到自己追住自己<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"3f8256007c76e4fc4f5645d17da87c233ff9d0fe","tid":443613,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:21:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢個宇宙好似被限制左速度 光速已經係極限?</blockquote><br />\n假設一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n接近光速 你開始穿越未來 你睇返後面會見到過去<br />\n<br />\n當你停低 你會發現你既時間快左</blockquote><br />\n冇錯冇錯<br />\n幾年前明珠台有個電視節目講可以用一輛接近光速嘅火車去未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f429266bd7eb4dd3751e854d317d9a0b387905","tid":443613,"uid":36026,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:24:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會望到一片黑暗 啲光唔夠你快 入唔到你眼 應該係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔一定 如果個地方有光同你唔平行咁行 總有機會同你隻眼相遇"},{"pid":"65bae3c6ca4c100b21facdafd0e01f6d77dc3408","tid":443613,"uid":118438,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:25:49.000Z","msg":"留名等物理權威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647ccea16e08bc29cd0dc7182fccabffb3caf0df","tid":443613,"uid":5822,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:27:11.000Z","msg":"老老柒柒<br />\n黑洞引力連光都吸到 係咪代表火速唔係最快？"},{"pid":"3338d3fa3898a62e23f19ea3caea16330a076b3d","tid":443613,"uid":149019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:28:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>影像係光折射 如果你快過光 就唔會睇到光折射 ie唔會睇到嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係覺得睇唔到野<br />\n或者人對眼係靠吸收光線去睇影像<br />\n如果你背向光源咁跑快過光<br />\n又要頭向後既，光唔夠快走入你對眼"},{"pid":"11f4c858393cca18081e89e5507fde8f0044a1ce","tid":443613,"uid":79829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:32:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢個宇宙好似被限制左速度 光速已經係極限?</blockquote><br />\n假設一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n接近光速 你開始穿越未來 你睇返後面會見到過去<br />\n<br />\n當你停低 你會發現你既時間快左</blockquote><br />\n冇錯冇錯<br />\n幾年前明珠台有個電視節目講可以用一輛接近光速嘅火車去未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係變慢左 當你速度差少少=光速，時間就會變慢 唔比你達到或者超越光速<br />\n<br />\n所以人地經歷左100年 你只係過左1個月<br />\n<br />\n唔通有某d文明 限制左呢個宇宙既文明發展速度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2786602746b88b69a5c773e64e0bc746597034b1","tid":443613,"uid":7306,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:32:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢個宇宙好似被限制左速度 光速已經係極限?</blockquote><br />\n假設一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n接近光速 你開始穿越未來 你睇返後面會見到過去<br />\n<br />\n當你停低 你會發現你既時間快左</blockquote><br />\n時間快左？唔明呢part</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cPM5mtU8PBY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcPM5mtU8PBY&d=LuN311ryFqadCm5aAoakJ54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=cae9ee5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cPM5mtU8PBY</a></blockquote><br />\n照條片咁講<br />\n咁如果用超高速錄影機係火車拍攝<br />\n咁咪會錄曬 咁多年來既影像？！"},{"pid":"fca9f13f97be308cc2e3403204813ea470c5d599","tid":443613,"uid":118438,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:33:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>影像係光折射 如果你快過光 就唔會睇到光折射 ie唔會睇到嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係覺得睇唔到野<br />\n或者人對眼係靠吸收光線去睇影像<br />\n如果你背向光源咁跑快過光<br />\n又要頭向後既，光唔夠快走入你對眼</blockquote><br />\n但會睇到之前嘅光？？"},{"pid":"dddd60556f6146c716a35e78dd6df57928cb55cf","tid":443613,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:35:49.000Z","msg":"咩都望唔到"},{"pid":"4ee22a058447769f11857be86e916fbe9081678c","tid":443613,"uid":124147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:36:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢個宇宙好似被限制左速度 光速已經係極限?</blockquote><br />\n假設一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n接近光速 你開始穿越未來 你睇返後面會見到過去<br />\n<br />\n當你停低 你會發現你既時間快左</blockquote><br />\n時間快左？唔明呢part</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cPM5mtU8PBY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcPM5mtU8PBY&d=LuN311ryFqadCm5aAoakJ54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=cae9ee5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cPM5mtU8PBY</a></blockquote><br />\n照條片咁講<br />\n咁如果用超高速錄影機係火車拍攝<br />\n咁咪會錄曬 咁多年來既影像？！</blockquote><br />\n部相機會影slow motion"},{"pid":"52a0c5ed122274546a9a1c291e3af550ddb1e757","tid":443613,"uid":136760,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:36:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>影像係光折射 如果你快過光 就唔會睇到光折射 ie唔會睇到嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係覺得睇唔到野<br />\n或者人對眼係靠吸收光線去睇影像<br />\n如果你背向光源咁跑快過光<br />\n又要頭向後既，光唔夠快走入你對眼</blockquote><br />\n但會睇到之前嘅光？？</blockquote><br />\n應該唔會睇唔到野<br />\n每一個位置都有光線存在<br />\n所以你快過光速跑向前，向後望應該會見到自己<br />\n其實即係睇返你身上投射出既影像"},{"pid":"1a51f7bb04bb23e1537effaa062829e8a6e4a1a6","tid":443613,"uid":79829,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:36:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>影像係光折射 如果你快過光 就唔會睇到光折射 ie唔會睇到嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係覺得睇唔到野<br />\n或者人對眼係靠吸收光線去睇影像<br />\n如果你背向光源咁跑快過光<br />\n又要頭向後既，光唔夠快走入你對眼</blockquote><br />\n但會睇到之前嘅光？？</blockquote><br />\n係 例如你而家睇到既太陽係8分鐘前既太陽<br />\n<br />\n光由太陽去到地球要8分鐘"},{"pid":"61e630aa9f01f8e5a9c94bdd5a32ceb68849444b","tid":443613,"uid":118438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:38:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>影像係光折射 如果你快過光 就唔會睇到光折射 ie唔會睇到嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係覺得睇唔到野<br />\n或者人對眼係靠吸收光線去睇影像<br />\n如果你背向光源咁跑快過光<br />\n又要頭向後既，光唔夠快走入你對眼</blockquote><br />\n但會睇到之前嘅光？？</blockquote><br />\n係 例如你而家睇到既太陽係8分鐘前既太陽<br />\n<br />\n光由太陽去到地球要8分鐘</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181ba81d9c92f46482205cf8793cefd4f645fc61","tid":443613,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:38:55.000Z","msg":"無光入到你眼，即係無野睇"},{"pid":"c3fb7dde6fdd3b935c8ed1850eac191cb9c24127","tid":443613,"uid":2446,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:39:13.000Z","msg":"首先跑得快過光速呢個假設已經唔成立"},{"pid":"25f0da39c2860d7ab74f8f4fcd26f6c0475c1c3a","tid":443613,"uid":56833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:40:02.000Z","msg":"黑色 乜都望唔到 因為光線都去唔到你隻眼 好似係"},{"pid":"98d329264563602a9393e4dcc8c12f70b502af15","tid":443613,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:49:11.000Z","msg":"你可能由起跑到停低果段時間<br />\n假設同一地點<br />\n起跑到停定之後你見到既可能係10年後既景物<br />\n而且返唔到轉頭"},{"pid":"138afa2e130038418c8b5694c7898eed6a3ab9ca","tid":443613,"uid":66276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T18:04:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a8a69eee9838e7dc9d947b72dc9f83ad89e2a28","tid":443613,"uid":66276,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T18:06:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b5e48605082431b76876ced422c707e6a6cb1527","tid":443613,"uid":61994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T18:06:49.000Z","msg":"影由光產生，你快過光，望後見到自己既殘影"},{"pid":"d238523d247a1ae42d39ad5813d426bf765842c5","tid":443613,"uid":3167,"like":0,